{"word":"καταδέχομαι","slug":"καταδέχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταδέχομαι</b></el> <el><b>-δέξομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to receive, admit</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to receive back, take home again</i>, <b>Oratt.</b>: —aor1 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>καταδεχθῆναι</el> in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> sense, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}